Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.90,0:01:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's the day I'm not showing up late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The next match for General \Nis in 10 days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more match to fight Daiba{/and it's match with ...}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba Ryo, just you wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet me outside{/in front of the building} in 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we took the long route{unsure if it means exactly the route and not "I chose to ride with you, albeit it takes longer"}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ditto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I like how this wind smells too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure wish I could feel this kind of wind every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make it happen!{/Let me do it!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I did the right thing by declining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You said something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a promise{[to give me a ride]} for tomorrow's morning too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Let's gallop it a little, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, today it's going to be hot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How ungracious of you, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You alright, Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch... Sorry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Master.\NYou should be more mindful{/careful} than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lucky to be in Ginya's care{to make this sound intimate, as if Ginya would always be here for her is essential for the next line's hidden meaning}, but with someone else, \Nthat would've destroyed{/shaken} your shop's good name{/reputation}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, why are you putting it this way{ [as if it's okay to douse me] - he misunderstoods her affectionate wording}{/what did you mean to say with that}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because it is this way. {exactly what it sounds like [- we're a pair]}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was just hot this morning, \Nbut the reason is {\i1}this way{\i0}.{[ - it's because you're lovebirds]}{he repeats yuri's wording "turns out it's this way after all" hence weird wording}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Master is saying it's this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will be this way too!\NOne Morning Set,{I hope he means "I will accept the "Morning" dish as apology since it's okay to douse me" because I'm out of options and 3 lines later also contributes to that} please!{good job, everyone, we can move on now}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This way,{\i0} after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:00.95,Song,,0,0,0,,Bronze-Silk Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your "Morning" is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... Is that Riichi? Alright... \NI'll get you{guess} like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My... Why did I even bother.{do whatever you please}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In 3 days, I defend my King's title{/a match for staying a King}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If things go favorably, \Nmy next match will be against Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo seems
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to have grown so faint...{/weak/frail}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:10.05,Song,,0,0,0,,Spinning Gears Publishing House
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud, \NI throw up my hands!{/this is hopeless}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Without warning, \Nthey passed 3 more advertisements to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting paid for this!{unsure, lit: salary/allowance is too much/very, maybe "we allow them too much"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it Ginya scribbling here{guess, there's no word mechishitsu, but close ones are "complete knowlegde" (like "does Ginya know what he's doing?") and "geological features" which is totally off the spot, yet both of those omit the "me" part, so I believe it's an onomatopeia and shares the root with "mechakucha", like "How unusual it is to see ginya writing earnestly"}? The speed \Nat which his hand moves is like that of a savvy{/average popular - Lit} writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible concentration. \NHas he caught fever or something?{no clue what this has to do with fever, maybe "he should be hot from moving that fast" or "He is sick hence he isn't acting like his usual self"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,2 pages done. \NNow it's yours to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but if you cut corners{/write superficially} because of the hurry, \NI'm not being lenient{/making you redo it}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No typos or misspells{/omitted characters/words} so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The pacing{I hope it's "tempo" and not something else} is also orderly{/not bad}. \NCan it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You "OK" it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a sec. \NUntil I read it to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The closing conclusion is articulate{I'm not sure how to handle it, it's "well-articulated/crisp/clear/exhaustive"} too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, quite engaging on the very first look.{unsure, maybe "Well, I've read quite enough already" meaning "I guess it's OK, you can be dismissed"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! \NThen, I'll leave you at that{/I'll be on my way}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the next topic?{Lit: [We're still do discuss] the research material to cover in the next [article]}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show up the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He put it together{/finished it} in a little more than 3 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya sure is one hit-and-miss fellow.{/You never know what to expect from Ginya/comes and goes/lives suddenly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \Nit felt like he's fighting some huge pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He, who can concentrate, \Nis never coming late.{/One who can focus his mind is never short of time/Lit: if you manage to concentrate your attention successfully, you can do it in/have time as well - methinks some proverb, maybe not}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That Ginya fellow is probably struggling \Nto overcome a demanding work assignment.{Lit: I wonder if he is amidst a close fight at work - he uses an explicit "tight contest" here, by which I think he refers to fighting in Slothium as "Ginya's work" as well}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't broke any promise this time.{Lit: because not giving any promise in particular - no fucking clue, maybe "that's why he is no longer promising me anything lately" or, which I stuck with, "I'm not waiting here for him now because he promised me to come as usual"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, you can be dismissed{/stop} now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Till later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my. \NShe seemed much more spirited{/felt good} just this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Ginya too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In some imperceptible way,{/Somehow/I feel that} \Nhe had a different look{/expression} in his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be because of a difficult{/tough} match in Slothium?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still getting distracted \Nby the surrounding noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't suffice{/Too self-indulgent}, Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrate your senses{/feelings} more, \Ncleanse{/sharpen/hone} your mind{/heart/soul}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba's defense of King is scheduled for the 5th{/for 2 days from now - there will be a visual fuckup at 9:21 so I'm going for a deliberate mistranslation here},\Nwhile Otonashi's match is on 15th{/in 10 days}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,15th?{/10 days?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll rush{/raise/hasten/reschedule} Otonashi Ginya's match \Nto 3 days from now and hold it as a double match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have already notified them \Naccording to current schedule...{/The notifications for the existing schedule had already been delivered}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, do it under the owner's fiat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, if that is your wish.{/will be done.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I exhausted my options for facilitating it.{/this is the best and utmost I can do to help you}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one from Slothium?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Schedule alteration notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In two days{/The day after tomorrow}, \Na double match coupled with King's defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten days{/week} sooner than planned?{/Sped up by 1 week}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win this match, \Ndo I get to challenge Daiba?{/does this mean Daiba's next?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.26,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting tomorrow too \N- Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{what the actual fuck lmao he rescheduled it to 10 days earlier, not a week, I'll change the rest of the lines accordingly, nobody knows japanese anyway}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world could have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In my experience{/As far as I know}, \Nthere has never been such a drastic change yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.54,Song,,0,0,0,,{Black Tea}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all,{I hope it's daiichi} the slotter has to{ go to the trouble to} adjust \Nhis life circumstances to the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But how am I to enhance my concentration then?{I'm guessing the context of "improving/raising my power of focus" here, especially in how this leads to him thinking of Oumi in the next scene - maybe "[cleaving your life to schedule] is a part of concentration training" or "that's why you should improve your focus"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Otonashi Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For Dr. Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Young doctor is on a business trip \Nfor academic conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi is really devoting his life undividedly \Nto the medical practice.{igyou may mean many things but this one makes most sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially{added} since that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse yourself losing in such a place
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the dream of challenging Daiba Ryo \Nwill forever remain a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That time, in order to make his retirement from Slothium worth it{/justified}, Oumi bet{/put ... into} his everything on this one final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You should, by leaps and bounds,{/ASAP} \Nrush{/run} straight up to{ [reach]} Daiba Ryo's spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But more than words that encouraged and empowered me, he transmitted{/conveyed} this pulsing{/beating} passion{/hot thoughts} straight into my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,before finally retiring from Slothium, I tried my utmost \Nto transmit as much of this message{ [of Daiba dying]} as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's but one thing I'm asking of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Be in a hurry, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no longer{added} any spare time to stand idly{/wait/spend away}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems both Oumi and Slothium \Nare trying to rush{/hurry} me, for whatever reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:06.69,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting tomorrow too \N- Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The number you have dialed is either out of reception zone{/somewhere the radio waves cannot reach it} \Nor the device is out of power{/or is turned off}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,By all means, I really want to investigate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's{/appears} as though even the Slothium itself \Nis trying to rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, even by just a day or two, \NI myself desire to fight Daiba sooner. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Otonashi does not have a match \Nplanned for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please check with the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I even approach this?{/What is going on}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri must be sure be mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Broke the promise to come to work{added} together \Non the second day{added}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he did.{/, after all/as expected}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, whatever I start{added}, \NI leave it half-done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya's stupid ass.{i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even having realized it now{ so late}, I still can't change a thing. \NI can only invest{/exhaust/do my best with} all my power in one battle in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, no other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I signed in as one of the Slothium participants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Slothium?{i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That place houses a superb slotter \Nby the name of Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting that fellow is, \Nfor the moment, my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreaming about fighting someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishibashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Just now, you had a face \Nlike you were about to throw yourself over{/take a plunge/jump}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I pondered over my major decision{/Lit: I decided upon a first-rate/important determination}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Do I pick{/choose} the job, \Nor do I pick the man?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This fellow sure is doing fine. \NHe also does a good job lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A man in such a period \Nis enjoying his prime years for making love.{guess - Lit: a man in such a time is when he is in good love/is a good time for him to love/be loving}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though he is glowing. \NYou can be confident in him, Yuri.{unsure, maybe it's he is confident or "you should be more confident"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to make sure \Nto win today's bout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Going somewhere{ out}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To Slothium?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm having an important rank-up match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,With a man by the name of Daiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No. But if I win today's match,\Nnext on the line will be Daiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm told Otonashi Ginya's schedule has been altered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If the queue{/arranged schedule/program/agenda - he is not using the exact word for schedule} is sped up by a great extent, \NI fear{/there's a risk} it may disorder{/unhinge/take a heavy toll on} his concentration{ abilities}.{/his concentration can go mad/get out of order}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Otonashi Ginya \Nis of that capricious{/soft/fragile} type?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I get your point.{/that is right too/I guess so/this may be true - this is ambiguous af}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The man you saw a prospect in{/you put your hopes on/anticipated/put trust in}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me in all earnestness{/frankness/honesty}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Slothium - \Nwhich one is more important?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not comparable. \NThe gauges{/dimensions/measures} are like heaven and earth{/completely different}.{this stupid daichi again, this time I cannot even write it off to "daiichi" so I'm completely clueless and will put "earth" in the other place in this sentence in a lack of better options, maybe it's "first off,"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that much. Yet if you had to choose, \Nwhich one would be your answer{/I want an answer}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Both are of {prime }importance to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I care for Yuri more than for anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then don't go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been thinking of retiring from Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,After that time, right? \NSince when you first met Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, hear me out! In Slothium, \Npeople who recognize me as a full-fledged{this line sucks but I don't see it anything but "[people recognizing me] as a fully developed person in slothium" but it may also be "as adult's, [we fight]" cueing to their tournament not being a child's play which it certainly may seem, and I'm still generally unsure about ichininmai, smt seems off here; some lines later, it points at "fully-formed/standing firmly and independently on his own feet" connotation}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,People, who recognize me as an opponent worth{added} fighting, \Nare waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That man was fighting foolhardily{/recklessly/frantically}, \N{[as though] }intending to subjugate the machine itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like as if he was tilting violently at windmills,{Lit: brandishing/wielding desperately the courageout but futile/doomed resistance / swinging the mantis axe - Lit; mine is not the exact translation, but I'm at a complete loss as for how to treat this one, maybe "flapping desperately in a fight he can't win"} \Nakin to a Don Quixote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was you who turned this Don Quixote \Ninto a full-fledged warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, "That youngster has all it takes{/may very well} to later{/one day} give me \Na once-in-a-lifetime{using "life" twice in 1 sentence sucks, but replacing the second life with "soul" would be unfaithful to ashita no joe} fight worth burning my life in."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya is going to meet all my expectations.{it's rather "he's meeting them" in present tense, but this does not consist with the next line} \NNo, he will outgrow{he uses specific word for "grow/mature"} the most optimistic of them.{/he will keep on growing much further than that}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to play{/see myself - 2 myselfs in one line} a rogue{unsure about this word's role here, maybe "I was criminally negligent towards you"} before, but with his fiery passion, \Nthis man made me grow to recognize myself as his rival,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so I want to answer appropriately \Nby throwing in all my might!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon enough, I'll get to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Such thoughts \Nmake my soul tremble in excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To bring your life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to a{/a sense of} fulfillment?{unsure, maybe it's "to feel your life completed/that you're accomplishing something while alive"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,An undeniable{/certain} sensation \Nthat outshines everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, I just truly wish for you\Nto understand my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your trust{/believe in me} and wait a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, between the Ultimate King Daiba Ryo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and King challenger Celestial{it sounds like amatsuma but that's not a real name and even though this announcer lady always uses de jure names, I'll make an allowance for this guy given how especially freak he is; methinks this should be another brainfuck reference, but I say 2deep4me} Junzo, \Na King defense battle will be held.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, two B-Block members will fight to qualify for challenging the King next - Otonashi Ginya and{/vs}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jackie Lee{gintama's jackie chan was funnier} will take part in Generals' match.{... will be held}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the double match ruleset, \Nthose matches will receive a simultaneous start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A double match, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, we'll have to keep an eye on both.{unsure, maybe "from which one we should never take eyes away?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Game start: 5 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,3, 2, 1. Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So much!?{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! More{/again} Gold Time for Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Skyrocketing into 5000 is viable now.{unsure, Lit: explosion 5000 coings is not a dream too}{/scoring 5000 in an explosion is no longer a dream}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He insane?{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This exceptional double match is astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,King is defending his grounds \Nas the next challenger is being decided.{Lit in King's battle, the new challenger is being decided - makes no sense, this is the best I could wrap it}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart has been pounding all the way{ until now}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The true opponent in my scope{/the opponent I'm aiming for}, Daiba Ryo,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya, by emerging{/appearing} here, \Nyou changed me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never yet felt so alive in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, as long as{/provided} you feel the magma splashing,{Lit: the sound of magma}{I hope it's magma} \Nconfined to the insides of my body{I hope it's body},{unclear - maybe it's otonashi's body, or even that he is addresing himself} you will win this bout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He unsheathed it!\NGod's finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on Renchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Time Rocket{guess, this bakushuchu is a mistery to me, but it sounds kinda sorta like "in a middle of explosion" though it's not the same explosion as some lines before, but rather "death from expl." so I used different kind of rocket-related word as well} \Nis leaving the atmosphere here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba, I'll be arriving at your place in no time.{/I'll climb to you soon already}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have climbed to the summit!{a play on words - this colloqually also means "be very engrossed/involved/passionate/infatuated"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya, I have long been waiting for a chance \Nto burn my life out unreservedly, fighting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's soon enough now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Otonashi cares not for the enemy in front of him, \Nfocusing on fighting Daiba instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The same is true for Daiba. \NIt's as though those two are in a King's battle already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to win and advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.30,Song,,0,0,0,,Ueno Train Station
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Game is concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Winner - Otonashi Ginya.
